{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_10_02",
  "title": "天動瑠依 2話 今度は私が応援する番です",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――年始特番当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The Day of the New Year’s Special",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "あけましておめでとうございます\nこんな早い時間に迎えに来ていただいてすみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Happy New Year.\nI’m sorry for having you pick me up so early.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.0019273917
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あけましておめでとう、瑠依。確かに早い時間だけど\nこれが俺の役目だし気にしないでくれ。今年もよろしく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Happy New Year‚ Rui. I know it’s early‚ but this is part of my job.\nSo don’t worry about it. Looking forward to working with you again this year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7437182013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "よろしくお願いします、{user}さん\n今年も頼りにしています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Likewise‚ {user}-san.\nI’ll be counting on you again this year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 22.3104530175
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "今日は私達トリエルの、新しい挑戦を\nしっかり見守って、応援していて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ please watch over and cheer on TRINITYAiLE\nas we take on a new challenge.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、応援しているし、精一杯支えるよ\nそれじゃあ、特番のスタジオに向かおう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I’m cheering for you‚ and I’ll support you with everything I’ve got.\nAlright then‚ let’s head to the special’s studio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.4122900484
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.6622900484
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "衣装とはいえ、元旦にこうして着物を着ると\n気が引き締まりますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if it’s just a costume‚ wearing a kimono like this on New Year’s Day\nreally puts me in the right mindset.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。朝からの長時間特番、しかも生放送だ\n移動もタイトだし、通常の振り袖とはいかないが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. It’s a long special starting early in the morning—and on top of that‚ it’s live.\nWith such tight travel schedules‚ we can’t go with a standard formal furisode.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.8545356908
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "今日の流れですけど、これからスタジオで番組開始\nいろいろな方の挑戦を見守りながら、MCを務めて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As for today’s rundown‚ the program will start in the studio.\nwe’ll serve as MC while watching over everyone’s challenges—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.4407256602
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "私と優とすみれも、生放送の中で、それぞれ挑戦を行う\n……ふぅ、私、今ドキドキしてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Yu‚ Sumire‚ and I will each take on our own challenges live.\n…Phew. My heart’s racing right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫か？　えっと、こういう時落ち着くには\nな、何か温かい飲み物でも……いや、仮眠……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you okay? Um‚ to calm down in situations like this—\nN-need some warm drink… or a quick nap…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.4618858807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.6367574849
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが慌ててどうするんですか？\nもう、少し落ち着いて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you panicking‚ {user}-san?\nCome on‚ calm down a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.8272887617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "す、すまない……大型特番の司会だからな……\n俺にも、緊張とドキドキがうつったみたいだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry… It’s a big special you’re hosting…\nI guess your nerves rubbed off on me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3126341216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.1177998699
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "慌ててる{user}さんを見ていたら\nなんだか少し落ち着いてきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seeing you flustered\nsomehow makes me feel calmer‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4701807959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.9438316819
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "『トリエルに翼を授けよう』の打ち合わせもありますし\n関係者のみなさんに、緊張した顔は見せられません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We also have the briefing for “Let’s Give Wings to TRINITYAiLE”\nI can’t show a nervous face to the staff.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.5418924056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "――さっき、先に現場に到着している\n有志の飛行機制作チームと、通話で話したんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Earlier‚ I spoke over a call\nwith the volunteer aircraft-building team that had already arrived on site.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1294154841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.246913862
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "天候や風向きを丁寧に教えてくれて\n最終調整をしながら、生放送も観てくださるそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They carefully explained the weather and wind conditions.\nThey’ll be watching the live broadcast while making final adjustments.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.1999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "自分の挑戦も頑張りますけど、まずは特番そのものを\n盛り上げないと、って気合いが入りました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll give my own challenge my all‚ of course—but more than that‚\nit got me pumped to make the special itself fired up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.5839892226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、堂々としている姿をファンに届けよう\nそろそろ時間だな、行こう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. Let’s show the fans your confident self.\nIt’s almost time—let’s go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.4333323161,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4645.623731399979,
          "startTime": 140.0789560475
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――年末特番開始後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—After the New Year’s Special Began",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.7456237314,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1587.7085847000103,
          "startTime": 140.3333323161
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "coast-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 140.0056206701
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（よし、瑠依達のMCは順調だったし）\n（スケジュール通り、現地に到着出来たな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Alright‚ Rui and the others’ MC work went smoothly.）\n（And we made it on site right on schedule.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.3666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、今からこの海に向かって\n高台から飛び立つんですね……ドキドキします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I’m taking off from that hill\ntoward the sea now… My heart’s pounding.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.321855247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "私が乗る飛行機は見ましたか？　凄いですよね\nいろいろなことを考えて、作ってくださって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Have you seen the aircraft I’ll be riding? It’s amazing.\nThey put so much thought into building it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.8666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "寒さを考えて、風避けを大きく作ってくれて\nペダルを漕ぐコックピットも、広さに余裕があって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They made the wind shield large to protect against the cold‚\nand the cockpit for pedaling is spacious too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.6031969804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "飛行機作りに関わった、みなさんの気持ちが\n沢山込められた機体でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was the aircraft filled with the care and passion of everyone\nwho worked on building it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.7002739069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ出番ですね。ドライスーツに着替えてきます\n最後は必ず着水しますから、防寒対策だそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s almost my turn. I’ll go change into the drysuit.\nI’ll definitely splash down at the end‚ so it’s for warmth.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.4333343506,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16738.01305699999,
          "startTime": 198.1713474076
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "……今日まで、鍛えられるだけ鍛えてきました\n準備万端です。私が羽ばたく姿、見ていて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’ve trained as much as I possibly could up to today.\nI’m fully prepared. Please watch me spread my wings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.0000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、ここから見てるよ\n頑張れ……瑠依なら高く、遠くまで飛べる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I’ll be watching from here.\nDo your best… You can fly high and far‚ Rui.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.5000010173,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5879.521608000005,
          "startTime": 204.3795226253
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12933.3312988,
          "startTime": 211.4333323161
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_futon-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14039.99802109999,
          "startTime": 212.5399990384
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの絆で……翼で！\n世界を翔けてみせる！！　テイクオーフ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With everyone’s bonds—our wings!\nI’ll soar across the world!! Takeoff!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.8000010173,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5578.648360200021,
          "startTime": 214.3786493775
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、瑠依。凄いじゃないか\nまさか、あそこから立て直すなんてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Great job‚ Rui. That was incredible.\nI never thought you’d recover from that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.4999898275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。ただ……立て直すというのは\n飛んでいる時のことでしょうか、それとも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. But… when you say “recover”—\nDo you mean during the flight‚ or…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.4333231609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだな。俺が間違ってカメラに映った時も\nうまく立て直してくれて助かったよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Right… when I accidentally got on camera‚\nyou handled that well too… it helped a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.5999898275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui021.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、気にしないで下さい。正直なところ、予想外\n過ぎて、私も少し慌ててしまいましたけど……っ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry about it. Honestly‚ it was unexpected‚\nSo even I panicked a little…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 241.9666564942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "……っ、あははっ、まさか{user}さんが\nあんなに子供みたいにはしゃぐなんて、あははっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ahaha‚ I never imagined you\nwould get that excited like a kid. Ahaha!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 249.9333231609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依の挑戦を見ていたら、俺まで熱くなってしまってな\nそ、それだけの力が、この挑戦にはあったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Watching your challenge fired me up too.\nT-that’s how powerful this challenge was.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.1333231609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui023.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、ありがとうございます\n思いっきり笑って、すっきりしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufufu‚ thank you.\nI laughed my heart out‚ and I feel refreshed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 271.1333231609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui024.m4a",
      "text": "飛距離はあまり伸びませんでしたけど、今の私の全力は\n出し切れました。だから、悔いはありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The distance wasn’t very far‚\nbut I gave it everything I have. I have no regrets.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.4470955395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui025.m4a",
      "text": "応援して、支えてくれて、考えて、気遣ってくれた\n{user}さんと、みなさんのおかげです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This was all thanks to {user}-san and everyone else\nwho cheered‚ supported‚ planned‚ and cared.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 287.5003436395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui026.m4a",
      "text": "番組が終わったら、機体を作ってくれた人達にお礼と\nそして私が見た景色を、伝えに行きたいと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After the program ends‚ I want to go thank the people who built the aircraft‚\nand tell them about the view I saw.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 295.2999898275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui027.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの想いを乗せて、私は空を飛んだ……\n本当に、いい『挑戦』が出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Carrying everyone’s feelings‚ I flew through the sky…\nIt truly was a wonderful “challenge.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 304.1000040691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui028.m4a",
      "text": "早く、優とすみれにも伝えたい。いえ、今日の特番を\n見てくれている人達、みんなに伝えたい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to tell Yu and Sumire soon—No‚\nI want to tell everyone watching today’s special…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 313.1000040691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。本当にお疲れ様、瑠依\n……それじゃ、そろそろスタジオに戻ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. You really did great‚ Rui.\n…Alright‚ let’s head back to the studio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 321.0666707357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui029.m4a",
      "text": "はい。優とすみれのチャレンジはこれからですし\n今度は私が応援する番です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Yu and Sumire’s challenges are still coming up.\nThis time‚ it’s my turn to cheer.",
        "id": ""
      },
